title: Meyer not yet revealing No. 1 Ohio State starting QB (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,385 Meyer not yet revealing No. 1 Ohio State starting QB (Yahoo Sports) Ohio State coach Urban Meyer isn't ready to publicly name a starting quarterback for the top-ranked Buckeyes' game at Rutgers on Saturday. Meyer must choose between Cardale Jones, who has started all seven games this season, and J.T. Barrett, the starter in 2014 before breaking his ankle in the final regular-season game against Michigan. Meyer was to meet with the two players Monday afternoon and announce his decision to them.
